Description: The Duplicate Records module, part of the larger SQUBA ecosystem, allows the user
    to provide a set of columns to include or exclude to define what should be considered duplication. 
    The module will then evaluate the proportion of rows and patients with duplicates, as well as the
    median number of duplicates per patient.
